00:00:11,762 --> 00:00:13,263
NEW SEMESTER,
NEW HAIR?

3
00:00:13,347 --> 00:00:14,806
I NEEDED A CHANGE.

4
00:00:14,890 --> 00:00:16,683
THE ONLY THING WORSE
THAN GOING BACK TO SCHOOL

5
00:00:16,767 --> 00:00:18,393
IS GOING BACK TO SCHOOL
IN WINTER.

6
00:00:18,477 --> 00:00:19,686
EMMA:
WELL, EVERY STEP WE TAKE,

7
00:00:19,770 --> 00:00:21,939
TAKES US ONE STEP CLOSER
TO GRADUATION.

8
00:00:23,315 --> 00:00:26,193
SPINNER:
OH, FINAL COUNTDOWN DUDES.

9
00:00:26,276 --> 00:00:29,696
EXACTLY 126 DAYS
'TIL GRADUATION -

10
00:00:30,822 --> 00:00:31,907
GIVE OR TAKE.

11
00:00:32,783 --> 00:00:35,536
WHY IS IT SO BUS-Y
AROUND HERE?

12
00:00:35,619 --> 00:00:36,995
WELCOME TO THE NEW WORLD

13
00:00:37,079 --> 00:00:38,997
OF DEGRASSI-LAKEHURST
COHABITATION.

14
00:00:39,081 --> 00:00:40,874
(SCHOOL BELL RINGS)

15
00:00:40,958 --> 00:00:42,209
STUDENT:
UGH, WATCH IT!

16
00:00:42,292 --> 00:00:43,293
HOW CAN THE PEOPLE
FROM THE SCHOOL

17
00:00:43,377 --> 00:00:45,128
THAT KILLED JT
BE COMING HERE?

18
00:00:45,212 --> 00:00:47,381
THEIR SCHOOL BURNS DOWN,
WE GET THEIR ASHES.

19
00:00:47,464 --> 00:00:48,882
GREAT IDEA,
SCHOOL BOARD.

20
00:00:48,966 --> 00:00:50,092
AND WHAT ARE THE CHANCES

21
00:00:50,175 --> 00:00:52,219
THERE'LL BE A SINGLE
CUTE GUY?

22
00:00:52,302 --> 00:00:53,679
WHAT? SORRY!

23
00:00:53,762 --> 00:00:56,306
WELL, MAYBE SOMEONE NEW
WILL STEAL DARCY AWAY

24
00:00:56,390 --> 00:00:58,809
FROM HIS EVIL HIGHNESS.

25
00:00:59,351 --> 00:01:01,228
AND THE GRASSHOPPER SAID,
"WHAT, HAROLD?"

26
00:01:01,311 --> 00:01:02,312
ALL:
(LAUGH)

27
00:01:02,855 --> 00:01:03,981
HIS EVIL HIGHNESS

28
00:01:04,064 --> 00:01:06,400
HAS BEEN DEFEATED
BY THE POWERS OF GOOD.

29
00:01:06,483 --> 00:01:07,818
I.E. ME.

30
00:01:08,527 --> 00:01:09,736
WE'RE IN LOVE
AND HE'S REFORMED.

31
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:11,071
I HAVE THAT EFFECT.

32
00:01:11,154 --> 00:01:12,072
IF ANYONE COULD,

33
00:01:12,155 --> 00:01:14,116
IT'S THE BLESSED VIRGIN,
DARCY.

34
00:01:14,199 --> 00:01:15,909
PETER:
DARCY, WE'RE IN SCHOOL.

35
00:01:15,993 --> 00:01:17,870
YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENS
IF MY MOM FINDS OUT.

36
00:01:17,953 --> 00:01:19,204
LOOK AROUND, PETER.

37
00:01:19,288 --> 00:01:21,206
YOUR MOM HAS BIGGER
THINGS ON HER MIND.

38
00:01:21,290 --> 00:01:22,749
AND DO YOU REALLY THINK
THE PRINCIPAL

39
00:01:22,833 --> 00:01:24,751
WOULD SEND HER SON
TO BOARDING SCHOOL?

40
00:01:24,835 --> 00:01:26,253
YEAH, WELL,
WHY NOW?

41
00:01:26,336 --> 00:01:27,588
WHAT'S THE RUSH?

42
00:01:27,671 --> 00:01:30,841
YOU'RE HAPPY WE HAVE TO KEEP
OUR RELATIONSHIP A SECRET?

43
00:01:30,924 --> 00:01:32,176
NAH, IT...
(EXHALES)

44
00:01:32,259 --> 00:01:33,010
I'M USED TO IT.

45
00:01:33,093 --> 00:01:35,220
PLUS, SNEAKING AROUND'S
KINDA HOT.

46
00:01:35,304 --> 00:01:36,263
I'M STARTING
TO THINK

47
00:01:36,346 --> 00:01:40,517
THAT YOU DON'T WANT PEOPLE
TO KNOW ABOUT US.

48
00:01:42,352 --> 00:01:42,978
(GASPS)

49
00:01:45,898 --> 00:01:46,440
(EXHALES)

50
00:01:46,523 --> 00:02:01,455
