00:02:30,108 --> 00:02:31,360
OKAY EVERYONE,
PLEASE GRAB A SEAT

54
00:02:31,443 --> 00:02:33,028
SO WE CAN BEGIN.

55
00:02:33,111 --> 00:02:35,322
UNTIL THE LAKEHURST
FIRE DAMAGE IS REPAIRED,

56
00:02:35,405 --> 00:02:38,075
YOU'LL BE EXPERIENCING
A LITTLE LESS ELBOW ROOM.

57
00:02:38,158 --> 00:02:39,076
NOW I KNOW,

58
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:40,661
AND I'M EXPECTING
ALL OF YOU

59
00:02:40,744 --> 00:02:43,580
TO MAKE OUR NEW GUESTS
FEEL RIGHT AT HOME.

60
00:02:43,664 --> 00:02:45,541
NOW DEGRASSI'S
HAD A LONG STANDING HISTORY

61
00:02:45,624 --> 00:02:47,167
OF BEING A WELCOMING
AND NURTURING ENVIRONMENT...

62
00:02:47,251 --> 00:02:49,711
SO...
WHY HAVEN'T WE TALKED?

63
00:02:49,795 --> 00:02:50,796
ABOUT WHAT?

64
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:52,881
ABOUT WHOLESOME,
CHRISTIAN YOU

65
00:02:52,965 --> 00:02:54,883
DATING DRUG-PLANTING,
STREET-RACING,

66
00:02:54,967 --> 00:02:55,968
BLACKMAILING PETER?

67
00:02:56,051 --> 00:02:58,136
AH, HELLO, MANNY?
RIGHT HERE.

68
00:02:58,220 --> 00:03:00,305
I'M NOT THAT GUY ANYMORE.
THAT WAS THE OLD ME.

69
00:03:00,389 --> 00:03:01,306
EXACTLY.

70
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:02,349
WHICH IS WHY
THERE'S NO REASON

71
00:03:02,432 --> 00:03:04,518
TO KEEP OUR
RELATIONSHIP SECRET.

72
00:03:04,601 --> 00:03:05,394
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?

73
00:03:05,477 --> 00:03:07,938
SHOVE MY MOM OUT OF THE WAY
AND MAKE AN ANNOUNCEMENT?

74
00:03:08,021 --> 00:03:09,815
FYI? I SAW YOU.

75
00:03:09,898 --> 00:03:12,025
FLIRTING WITH THOSE GIRLS
FROM LAKEHURST.

76
00:03:12,109 --> 00:03:13,318
AND IF YOU EVER
WALK OFF-

77
00:03:13,402 --> 00:03:14,736
GUYS! SHHH!

78
00:03:16,905 --> 00:03:18,031
DARCE, YOU'RE MY GIRL,

79
00:03:18,115 --> 00:03:19,825
WHAT MORE PROOF
DO YOU NEED?

80
00:03:19,908 --> 00:03:21,535
YOU'RE THE FORMER
CRIMINAL MASTERMIND.

81
00:03:21,618 --> 00:03:23,036
THINK OF SOMETHING.

82
00:03:27,958 --> 00:03:30,169
SIMPSON:
OFF TO CLASS, GUYS.
OFF TO CLASS.

83
00:03:30,252 --> 00:03:32,129
AH, TOBY ISAACS,

84
00:03:32,212 --> 00:03:34,006
READY FOR ONE LAST SEMESTER
AS MY DIGI-GURU?

85
00:03:34,089 --> 00:03:35,883
JOHNNY:
DIGI-WIENER.

86
00:03:35,966 --> 00:03:37,509
DIMARCO, RIGHT?

87
00:03:40,137 --> 00:03:42,222
SOMETHING TO SAY?

88
00:03:42,306 --> 00:03:42,806
NO, SIR.

89
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:45,225
REALLY?
'CUZ I HEARD SOMETHING.

90
00:03:45,309 --> 00:03:47,352
SOUNDED IMPORTANT,
ACTUALLY.

91
00:03:47,436 --> 00:03:49,479
(SCHOOL BELL RINGS)

92
00:03:50,022 --> 00:03:52,107
OFF TO CLASS, GUYS.

93
00:03:56,153 --> 00:03:59,656
(STUDENTS CHATTER,
CELL PHONE RINGS)

94
00:04:00,991 --> 00:04:01,992
CROWDED MUCH?

95
00:04:02,075 --> 00:04:04,369
I FEEL OUT OF PLACE
IN MY OWN CAF'.

96
00:04:04,453 --> 00:04:06,705
SO, HAS PETER
COME UP WITH A MASTER PLAN

97
00:04:06,788 --> 00:04:08,207
FOR YOU TWO GOING PUBLIC,
YET?

98
00:04:08,290 --> 00:04:09,625
NO. BUT IT WOULD
PROBABLY HELP

99
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:11,960
IF I COULD EVEN FIND THAT
CHARMING BOYFRIEND OF MINE.

100
00:04:12,044 --> 00:04:14,421
I THINK I FOUND MINE.

101
00:04:14,505 --> 00:04:16,256
(MUTED CHATTER)

102
00:04:17,174 --> 00:04:19,384
HEY,
ARE THESE SEATS TAKEN?

103
00:04:19,468 --> 00:04:21,053
UH, SIT HERE.

104
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:24,640
MANNY:
THANK YOU.

105
00:04:26,058 --> 00:04:27,100
I'M, SAV,
BY THE WAY.

106
00:04:27,184 --> 00:04:29,853
MANNY.
AND THIS IS, DARCY.

107
00:04:30,646 --> 00:04:31,480
HEY.

108
00:04:34,858 --> 00:04:36,109
JANE. HI.

109
00:04:36,777 --> 00:04:37,736
I WAS JUST TELLIN' JANE

110
00:04:37,819 --> 00:04:38,779
THAT WE SHOULD ROUND UP
SOME PEOPLE

111
00:04:38,862 --> 00:04:40,239
AND GO SNOWBOARDING
THIS WEEKEND.

112
00:04:40,322 --> 00:04:41,990
AND I WAS JUST TELLING SAV

113
00:04:42,074 --> 00:04:43,450
THAT NOBODY'D BE
INTERESTED.

114
00:04:43,534 --> 00:04:45,410
AH, WE MIGHT BE.
RIGHT, DARCY?

115
00:04:45,494 --> 00:04:48,247
UH, SOUNDS LIKE
A BLAST OF COLD.

116
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:51,291
BESIDES,
I'VE GOT A CHURCH RETREAT.

117
00:04:51,375 --> 00:04:54,127
(SMIRKS)
GOTTA GET YOUR BIBLE ON?

118
00:04:54,211 --> 00:04:55,420
IT'S JUST HER
NEVER-ENDING SEARCH

119
00:04:55,504 --> 00:04:57,631
FOR ETERNAL HAPPINESS.

120
00:04:57,714 --> 00:04:59,424
HAS SHE CHECKED UNDER
HER EXTENSIONS?

121
00:04:59,508 --> 00:05:03,887
DARCY:
UH! NO, BUT THERE IT IS
BEHIND YOUR GIGANTIC RUMP!

122
00:05:03,971 --> 00:05:05,305
(CHUCKLES)

123
00:05:09,434 --> 00:05:10,936
(FOOD AND TRAY CLATTER)

124
00:05:11,019 --> 00:05:13,605
STUDENTS:
(STUNNED GASPS)

125
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:17,192
HATZILAKOS:
DARCY EDWARDS,

126
00:05:17,276 --> 00:05:19,486
PLEASE REPORT TO THE PRINCIPLES
OFFICE IMMEDIATELY.

127
00:05:19,570 --> 00:05:21,446
WAIT,
THAT'S YOU?

128
00:05:21,530 --> 00:05:24,658
BUT YOU SEEM LIKE
SUCH A GOOD GIRL.

129
00:05:24,741 --> 00:05:27,494
HMPH,
YOU BETTER CLEAN THAT UP.

130
00:05:27,578 --> 00:05:29,246
LOVE OUR NEW GUESTS.

131
00:05:34,835 --> 00:05:36,712
IS THIS BIT OF FILTH
TAKEN?

132
00:05:36,795 --> 00:05:39,089
TRYING TO FEEL ME UP,
TOAD?

133
00:05:40,465 --> 00:05:42,801
THIS IS OUR HALL,
THESE ARE OUR LOCKERS.

134
00:05:42,885 --> 00:05:44,636
THESE ARE OUR...

135
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:47,264
CRAPPY MOTIVATIONAL POSTERS.

136
00:05:47,347 --> 00:05:49,516
THEY HAVE NO RIGHT
TO TAKE THIS FROM US.

137
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,101
LAKEHURST WAS FORCED
TO COME HERE.

138
00:05:51,185 --> 00:05:52,352
IT WASN'T
THEIR CHOICE.

139
00:05:52,436 --> 00:05:54,688
SO YOU'RE OKAY WITH
JT'S KILLERS BEING HERE?

140
00:05:54,771 --> 00:05:56,565
I FEEL A PODCAST
COMING ON.

141
00:05:56,648 --> 00:05:58,150
I'M SERIOUS.

142
00:05:58,233 --> 00:05:59,693
TOBES, I'M NEVER
GONNA BE OKAY

143
00:05:59,776 --> 00:06:01,862
WITH THE FACT
THAT JT'S GONE,

144
00:06:01,945 --> 00:06:04,364
BUT LAKEHURST
DIDN'T KILL HIM.

145
00:06:04,448 --> 00:06:06,491
ONE PSYCHO DID
AND HE'S IN JAIL.

146
00:06:06,575 --> 00:06:07,951
JOHNNY DIMARCO'S HERE.

147
00:06:08,035 --> 00:06:09,578
HE WAS THERE
WHEN JT GOT STABBED

148
00:06:09,661 --> 00:06:10,913
AND WHAT HAPPENS TO HIM?

149
00:06:10,996 --> 00:06:12,372
NOTHING.

150
00:06:12,456 --> 00:06:14,166
DR. MARTIN LUTHER KING SAID,

151
00:06:14,249 --> 00:06:15,292
"RETURNING VIOLENCE
FOR VIOLENCE

152
00:06:15,375 --> 00:06:17,544
MULTIPLIES VIOLENCE,
ADDING DEEPER DARKNESS

153
00:06:17,628 --> 00:06:20,506
TO A NIGHT ALREADY
DEVOID OF STARS".

154
00:06:20,589 --> 00:06:22,424
LET IT GO, TOBY.

155
00:06:25,719 --> 00:06:27,054
(KNOCKS ON DOOR)

156
00:06:27,137 --> 00:06:28,305
COME IN.

157
00:06:29,556 --> 00:06:31,225
SO, PETER SAYS THERE'S
SOMETHING THAT YOU TWO

158
00:06:31,308 --> 00:06:32,476
WANNA TELL ME?

159
00:06:33,143 --> 00:06:34,394
MOM, UM...

160
00:06:34,478 --> 00:06:36,146
YOU KNOW HOW I LIKE
KETCHUP ON MY BROCCOLI?

161
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:37,606
SHOULDN'T GO TOGETHER,
RIGHT?

162
00:06:37,689 --> 00:06:39,816
UH, WELL THAT'S A LOT
LIKE ME AND DARCY.

163
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:40,567
WE'VE BEEN SORTA-

164
00:06:40,651 --> 00:06:43,737
I THINK HE'S TRYING TO SAY
THAT WE'RE TOGETHER.

165
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:46,323
AND WE DON'T WANT KEEP IT
A SECRET ANY MORE.

166
00:06:46,406 --> 00:06:47,741
HAVE YOUR PARENTS
GIVEN THEIR BLESSING?

167
00:06:47,824 --> 00:06:48,825
OH, SURE,

168
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:50,077
AS LONG AS WE OBEY
THE RULE OF CHASTITY,

169
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,203
THEY'RE HAPPY.

170
00:06:51,286 --> 00:06:53,914
WE WANT TO BE HONEST,
OR WHATEVER.

171
00:06:53,997 --> 00:06:56,583
WELL, PETER'S, BEHAVIOUR
HAS TURNED AROUND

172
00:06:56,667 --> 00:06:58,585
AND I THINK I KNOW WHY.

173
00:06:58,669 --> 00:06:59,753
SO WHAT CAN I SAY?

174
00:06:59,837 --> 00:07:00,587
HE'S A LUCKY KID.

175
00:07:00,671 --> 00:07:01,672
(JOYFUL GASP)

176
00:07:02,965 --> 00:07:04,424
BUT IF YOU GIVE ME
ANY REASON...

177
00:07:04,508 --> 00:07:05,259
I'LL RECONSIDER.

178
00:07:05,342 --> 00:07:07,261
OH, WE'LL BE ANGELS.
PROMISE.

179
00:07:07,344 --> 00:07:08,428
(PHONE RINGS)

180
00:07:12,933 --> 00:07:13,976
LAKEHURST STUDENT:
YOU WANNA MEET UP AT THE DOT?

181
00:07:14,059 --> 00:07:15,435
THE DEGRASSI PLACE?
WHAT ARE YOU ON?

182
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,311
I'LL SEE YOU
AT THE BREAK ROOM.

183
00:07:16,395 --> 00:07:18,480
LAKEHURST STUDENT:
ALL RIGHT.

184
00:07:18,564 --> 00:07:20,858
SO, LAKEHURST BURNS
TO THE GROUND.

185
00:07:20,941 --> 00:07:22,234
HOW APPROPRIATE.

186
00:07:22,317 --> 00:07:22,776
BELIEVE ME,

187
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:24,111
I WISH I WERE ANYWHERE
BUT THIS DUMP.

188
00:07:24,194 --> 00:07:26,905
YEAH,
THAT MAKES TWO OF US.

189
00:07:28,866 --> 00:07:30,742
WAIT, YOU'RE THE GUY
WE ROLLED LAST SEMESTER.

190
00:07:30,826 --> 00:07:32,202
AWE, MAN,
I'M OVER THAT, ALL RIGHT.

191
00:07:32,286 --> 00:07:33,245
HOW 'BOUT A PEACE TREATY?

192
00:07:33,328 --> 00:07:36,290
NOT UNLESS YOU SAY
YOU'RE SORRY.

193
00:07:36,373 --> 00:07:37,624
FINE.

194
00:07:37,708 --> 00:07:39,376
I'M SORRY I CALLED YOU
A DIGI-WIENER

195
00:07:39,459 --> 00:07:40,961
AND KICKED YOUR ASS.

196
00:07:41,044 --> 00:07:42,504
YOU STOOD THERE
WHILE YOUR FRIEND

197
00:07:42,588 --> 00:07:45,340
STABBED MY FRIEND
TO DEATH.

198
00:07:53,015 --> 00:07:56,059
(BASKETBALL BOUNCES,
SNEAKERS SQUEAK)

199
00:07:56,685 --> 00:07:58,812
UM, IF WE'RE GOING
TO BE ONE SQUAD?

200
00:07:58,896 --> 00:08:00,647
I NOMINATE MYSELF
AS CO-CAPTAIN.

201
00:08:00,731 --> 00:08:03,150
(SARCASTIC HUFF)
PLEASE, JOB'S TAKEN.

202
00:08:03,233 --> 00:08:05,152
WARM UPS, PEOPLE!

203
00:08:07,154 --> 00:08:09,114
I HAVE AN ANNOUNCEMENT.

204
00:08:09,198 --> 00:08:11,200
ARE YOU A VAMPIRE?

205
00:08:12,409 --> 00:08:14,203
ME AND PETER,
WE'RE OFFICIAL.

206
00:08:14,286 --> 00:08:17,497
AND HIS MOM IS TOTALLY COOL
WITH US BEING US.

207
00:08:17,581 --> 00:08:19,333
THAT'S KIND OF AMAZING.

208
00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:21,835
SO, YOU'RE OKAY
WITH IT, TOO?

209
00:08:21,919 --> 00:08:24,046
AS LONG AS
YOU'RE HAPPY.

210
00:08:24,129 --> 00:08:28,300
SPEAKING OF HAPPY?
I'M IN A SNOWBOARDING MOOD.

211
00:08:28,383 --> 00:08:30,844
A SNOWBOARDING MOOD,
OR A SAV MOOD?

212
00:08:30,928 --> 00:08:32,638
ALREADY WITH
THE BOY CRAZY?

213
00:08:32,721 --> 00:08:34,681
SAV, SHMAV,
IT'LL BE FUN.

214
00:08:34,765 --> 00:08:36,266
UNLESS DITCHING
CHURCH RETREAT

215
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:37,893
GETS YOU STRUCK
BY LIGHTNING?

216
00:08:37,976 --> 00:08:41,522
EVEN IF I WERE TO RISK
DIVINE ELECTROCUTION?

217
00:08:41,605 --> 00:08:43,357
IT WOULD BE
TO SPEND TIME HERE

218
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,442
WITH MY BOYFRIEND.

219
00:08:46,944 --> 00:08:48,362
MRS. EDWARDS:
(SIGHS)

220
00:08:48,445 --> 00:08:50,989
WHAT'S TAKING SO LONG?
WHERE'S DARCY?

221
00:08:51,073 --> 00:08:52,199
CAN I HELP YOU?

222
00:08:52,282 --> 00:08:53,867
UH, MY DAUGHTER'S
ON SPIRIT SQUAD.

223
00:08:53,951 --> 00:08:55,827
CHAUFFEUR SERVICE,
YOU KNOW.

224
00:08:55,911 --> 00:08:56,745
DARCY:
HI!

225
00:08:57,579 --> 00:08:59,331
SORRY, I'M LATE!
AH, LET'S GO!

226
00:08:59,414 --> 00:09:02,376
OH, I'M DAPHNE HATZILAKOS,
DARCY'S PRINCIPAL.

227
00:09:02,459 --> 00:09:04,044
AND YOU KNOW MY SON,
PETER?

228
00:09:04,127 --> 00:09:05,838
OH, WE KNOW YOUR SON.

229
00:09:06,421 --> 00:09:09,508
HATZILAKOS:
GREAT, WELL,
I WAS HOPING WE'D MEET.

230
00:09:09,591 --> 00:09:11,468
UM, DARCY'S NOT IN TROUBLE,
IS SHE?

231
00:09:11,552 --> 00:09:13,095
OH, NO-NO,

232
00:09:13,178 --> 00:09:14,888
BUT IF MY SON AND YOUR DAUGHTER
ARE GOING TO BE AN ITEM?

233
00:09:14,972 --> 00:09:17,140
IT'S BEST THAT WE HAVE
EACH OTHER ON SPEED-DIAL.

234
00:09:17,224 --> 00:09:18,267
OH, NO-NO-NO-NO-NO.

235
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:19,852
THERE MUST BE SOME
MISUNDERSTANDING.

236
00:09:19,935 --> 00:09:21,728
DARCY,
IS NOT DATING YOUR SON.

237
00:09:21,812 --> 00:09:23,981
MR. EDWARDS:
DARCY TOLD US HE LEFT HER
TO WALK HOME IN THE RAIN

238
00:09:24,064 --> 00:09:27,359
AFTER BEING CITED FOR DRIVING
WITHOUT A LICENSE?

239
00:09:27,442 --> 00:09:30,279
YES, AND I SEE
SHE SURVIVED.

240
00:09:31,446 --> 00:09:32,573
MR. EDWARDS:
AND WHAT ABOUT
THOSE PHOTOS HE TOOK

241
00:09:32,656 --> 00:09:34,908
AND SENT TO HIS PERVERTED
FRIENDS ON THE INTERNET?

242
00:09:34,992 --> 00:09:36,577
THAT WAS HER IDEA.

243
00:09:36,660 --> 00:09:38,829
HAZILAKOS:
LOOK, I KNOW
PETER IS NO ANGEL,

244
00:09:38,912 --> 00:09:39,746
BUT I AM DOING MY BEST.

245
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:43,792
MS. HATZILAKOS,
I'M SURE YOUR SON IS A HANDFUL.

246
00:09:44,668 --> 00:09:47,254
I CAN HANDLE MY SON,
MR. EDWARDS.

247
00:09:47,337 --> 00:09:49,590
WELL, MAYBE IF YOU
AND MR. HATZILAKOS

248
00:09:49,673 --> 00:09:50,716
WERE STILL TOGETHER...

249
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,466
MOM!

250
00:09:55,012 --> 00:09:57,347
VERY NICE TO MEET YOU.

251
00:10:01,518 --> 00:10:03,270
DARCY,
DO SOMETHING!

252
00:10:09,526 --> 00:10:10,444
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

253
00:10:10,527 --> 00:10:11,820
MRS. EDWARDS:
DARCY?

254
00:10:12,529 --> 00:10:14,198
ARE YOU READY?

255
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:17,075
THE BUS IS LEAVING!

256
00:10:17,576 --> 00:10:20,454
(CLEARS THROAT)
OUR MINIVAN
CAN GO WITHOUT ME.

257
00:10:20,537 --> 00:10:22,372
NOBODY'S GOING ON
THE RETREAT WITHOUT YOU.

258
00:10:22,456 --> 00:10:24,333
(COUGHS)
I THINK I'M COMING DOWN
WITH A COLD.

259
00:10:24,416 --> 00:10:26,043
CAN'T I JUST STAY HOME?

260
00:10:26,126 --> 00:10:27,169
MRS. EDWARDS:
BUT YOU ALWAYS HAVE
SO MUCH FUN

261
00:10:27,252 --> 00:10:28,587
ON THE RETREAT.

262
00:10:29,046 --> 00:10:30,339
I DON'T WANT TO
SPREAD MY GERMS

263
00:10:30,422 --> 00:10:32,424
AND I HAVE HOMEWORK,
NEW CHEERS AND-

264
00:10:32,508 --> 00:10:34,468
OH, I DON'T KNOW,
SWEETIE.

265
00:10:34,551 --> 00:10:36,970
STAYING BY YOURSELF?
OVERNIGHT?

266
00:10:37,054 --> 00:10:38,639
MOM, I'M SEVENTEEN!

267
00:10:40,724 --> 00:10:41,975
(EXHALES)

268
00:10:42,059 --> 00:10:43,310
OKAY.

269
00:10:43,393 --> 00:10:45,270
YOU'VE GOT A GOOD HEAD
ON YOUR SHOULDERS.

270
00:10:45,354 --> 00:10:46,855
AND WE TRUST YOU.

271
00:10:46,939 --> 00:10:47,940
THANKS, MOM.

272
00:10:48,023 --> 00:10:49,650
MRS. EDWARDS:
OKAY, REST UP.
WE'LL BE CHECKING IN;

273
00:10:49,733 --> 00:10:51,109
YOU HAVE OUR NUMBERS.

274
00:10:51,193 --> 00:10:53,403
AND WE'LL BE BACK LATER
TOMORROW AFTERNOON.

275
00:10:53,487 --> 00:10:54,363
OKAY.

276
00:11:02,162 --> 00:11:03,914
(OVERLAPPING CHATTER)

277
00:11:08,544 --> 00:11:09,628
DARCY:
(HURRIED PANTING)

278
00:11:09,711 --> 00:11:11,171
THERE YOU ARE,
ALL JUST IN TIME.

279
00:11:11,255 --> 00:11:12,881
YEAH, I HAD TO WAIT
FOR MY PARENTS TO LEAVE.

280
00:11:12,965 --> 00:11:13,882
I TAKE IT
THE CHURCHERSONS

281
00:11:13,966 --> 00:11:15,676
AREN'T COOL WITH
UNSUPERVISED WINTER FUN?

282
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:17,261
THAT WOULD BE A "NO",
BUT YOU TAUGHT ME

283
00:11:17,344 --> 00:11:19,346
EVERYTHING THERE IS TO KNOW
ABOUT CALL FORWARDING.

284
00:11:19,429 --> 00:11:21,265
HAVE YOU SEEN PETER?

285
00:11:21,348 --> 00:11:21,807
NO.

286
00:11:22,432 --> 00:11:23,892
UGH, I HAVE VOICEMAIL.

287
00:11:23,976 --> 00:11:25,227
AH, PETER, IT'S ME.

288
00:11:25,310 --> 00:11:26,311
I'M ON MY WAY
TO MOUNT HURON.

289
00:11:26,395 --> 00:11:27,980
THE NEXT BUS LEAVES
IN AN HOUR,

290
00:11:28,063 --> 00:11:28,897
PLEASE COME.

291
00:11:28,981 --> 00:11:32,317
I PROMISE I'LL MAKE IT
WORTH YOUR WHILE.

292
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:34,903
HURRY UP!

293
00:11:37,823 --> 00:11:39,700
IF LAKEHURST CAST-OFFS
LIKE JOHNNY DIMARCO

294
00:11:39,783 --> 00:11:40,784
THINK THAT I'M GONNA
PERSONALLY

295
00:11:40,868 --> 00:11:42,202
WELCOME THEM TO DEGRASSI?

296
00:11:42,286 --> 00:11:44,329
WAKE UP!
IT AIN'T GONNA HAPPEN!

297
00:11:44,413 --> 00:11:46,123
AND IF ANYONE
HAS A PROBLEM WITH THAT?

298
00:11:46,206 --> 00:11:49,626
REMEMBER:
NOBODY MESSES WITH TOBY ISAACS.

299
00:11:53,005 --> 00:11:54,631
(PROGRESS BAR BEEPS)

300
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:07,311
♪♪♪

301
00:12:08,145 --> 00:12:09,146
HERE.

302
00:12:09,229 --> 00:12:10,147
WEDGE YOUR FOOT IN.

303
00:12:10,230 --> 00:12:11,523
UGH, I'VE NEVER
DONE THIS BEFORE.

304
00:12:11,607 --> 00:12:12,441
I'M GONNA BREAK
MY NECK.

305
00:12:12,524 --> 00:12:14,651
IT'S NOT AS SCARY
AS IT LOOKS, OKAY.

306
00:12:14,735 --> 00:12:16,695
IF YOU LEARN NOW,
YOU'LL NEVER FORGET.

307
00:12:16,778 --> 00:12:19,531
RIGHT FOOT FIRST?
ARE YOU GOOFY?

308
00:12:19,615 --> 00:12:20,866
NEVER MIND.
(SMIRKS)

309
00:12:20,949 --> 00:12:22,242
HEY, UM,
KILLER PARTY TONIGHT.

310
00:12:22,326 --> 00:12:23,911
GUARANTEED RAGER,
IF YOU'RE STICKING AROUND

311
00:12:23,994 --> 00:12:24,745
'TIL THE LAST BUS.

312
00:12:24,828 --> 00:12:25,829
HUH, FUNNY,

313
00:12:25,913 --> 00:12:27,206
I WAS JUST WONDERING
WHEN THE NEXT BUS LEAVES

314
00:12:27,289 --> 00:12:28,290
TO GO HOME.

315
00:12:28,373 --> 00:12:29,166
(CELL PHONE RINGS)

316
00:12:29,249 --> 00:12:30,375
STOP TOUCHING.

317
00:12:30,459 --> 00:12:31,627
(PHONE RINGS)

318
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:32,878
PETER?
THANK GOSH!

319
00:12:32,961 --> 00:12:34,922
I'M SO SORRY I COULDN'T
STAND UP TO MY PARENTS.

320
00:12:35,005 --> 00:12:37,090
PLEASE JUST TELL ME YOU'RE
NOT CALLING TO BREAK UP.

321
00:12:37,174 --> 00:12:38,759
WELL, YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S
SUPPOSED TO HAVE FAITH.

322
00:12:38,842 --> 00:12:40,093
DARCY:
OH! YOU MADE IT!

323
00:12:40,177 --> 00:12:42,095
YEAH, I PULLED
THE MOM'S HOUSE/DAD'S HOUSE

324
00:12:42,179 --> 00:12:43,597
SHELL GAME.

325
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:45,057
YOU SAID YOU'D MAKE IT
WORTH MY WHILE.

326
00:12:45,140 --> 00:12:46,433
AND DID YOU HEAR ABOUT
THE PARTY TONIGHT?

327
00:12:46,517 --> 00:12:48,560
PETER:
YEAH. BONUS!

328
00:12:50,562 --> 00:12:52,356
MANNY:
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.
I'M NOT HELPING YOU ANYMORE.

329
00:12:53,398 --> 00:13:07,454
♪♪♪

330
00:13:07,538 --> 00:13:22,177
♪♪♪

331
00:13:22,261 --> 00:13:38,402
♪♪♪

332
00:13:38,485 --> 00:13:40,237
(HOCKEY STICKS CLANK)

333
00:13:43,907 --> 00:13:45,158
LIBERTY:
TOBY!

334
00:13:45,242 --> 00:13:47,870
"LAKEHURST ARE BUNCH OF MOUTH
BREATHING NEANDERTHALS?"

335
00:13:47,953 --> 00:13:49,746
I COULDN'T AGREE MORE.

336
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:50,747
I HEARD YOUR PODCAST.

337
00:13:50,831 --> 00:13:52,499
HOW IS NAME-CALLING
SUPPOSED TO HELP?

338
00:13:52,583 --> 00:13:55,586
IT'S NOT NAME-CALLING.
IT'S SCIENTIFIC CLASSIFICATION.

339
00:13:55,669 --> 00:13:56,712
I WAS GOING TO ASK YOU
TO HEAD UP

340
00:13:56,795 --> 00:13:57,963
THE INTEGRATION COMMITTEE,

341
00:13:58,046 --> 00:14:00,340
BUT YOUR PERSONAL VENDETTA
ISN'T HELPING.

342
00:14:00,424 --> 00:14:02,676
YEAH WELL, MAYBE SOME PEOPLE
DON'T WANT TO INTEGRATE.

343
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:03,677
LIBERTY:
(SIGHS)

344
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,094
CAR.

345
00:14:08,724 --> 00:14:09,892
(ENGINE WHIRS)

346
00:14:10,809 --> 00:14:11,643
DANNY:
CHECK IT.

347
00:14:11,727 --> 00:14:13,645
LAKEHURST NINERS.

348
00:14:16,857 --> 00:14:19,026
WANNA GO BUST HEADS?

349
00:14:20,944 --> 00:14:21,987
LATER, OKAY?

350
00:14:22,070 --> 00:14:23,197
IS THIS WHAT YOU WANT?

351
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:24,573
AN ONGOING WAR.

352
00:14:25,365 --> 00:14:28,368
YOU REMEMBER HOW THAT ENDED
LAST TIME.

353
00:14:28,452 --> 00:14:30,245
(HOCKEY STICKS CLANK)

354
00:14:30,329 --> 00:14:31,288
(GLASS SHATTERS)

355
00:14:31,371 --> 00:14:33,707
(ROCK MUSIC PLAYS)
(CHATTER)

356
00:14:34,958 --> 00:14:36,210
MANNY:
DITCHING THE CHURCH RETREAT.

357
00:14:36,293 --> 00:14:37,211
LYING TO YOUR PARENTS.

358
00:14:37,294 --> 00:14:37,878
SNEAKING OUT.

359
00:14:37,961 --> 00:14:39,213
YOU KNOW,
YOU DON'T HAVE TO COMMIT

360
00:14:39,296 --> 00:14:41,465
ALL SEVEN DEADLY SINS
IN ONE NIGHT.

361
00:14:41,548 --> 00:14:43,509
HEY, I'M NOT DRINKING,
AM I?

362
00:14:43,592 --> 00:14:44,927
BESIDES, NONE OF THIS
WOULD BE NECESSARY

363
00:14:45,010 --> 00:14:46,386
IF MY PARENTS
HADN'T BANNED ME

364
00:14:46,470 --> 00:14:47,471
FROM SEEING PETER.

365
00:14:47,554 --> 00:14:49,598
WHEN WILL PARENTS
EVER LEARN?

366
00:14:49,681 --> 00:14:51,391
FORBIDDING THINGS
IS AN APHRODISIAC.

367
00:14:51,475 --> 00:14:53,018
(GIGGLES)
TOTALLY.

368
00:14:54,686 --> 00:14:56,647
(PARTY MUSIC CONTINUES)

369
00:15:00,943 --> 00:15:02,861
(DISGUSTED GROAN)

370
00:15:03,987 --> 00:15:07,324
DARCY:
FINALLY I HAVE YOU
ALL TO MYSELF.

371
00:15:08,575 --> 00:15:10,118
PETER:
AND THERE'S NOTHING
OUR PARENTS CAN DO ABOUT IT.

372
00:15:10,202 --> 00:15:10,953
DARCY:
UGH. YOU WERE RIGHT.

373
00:15:11,036 --> 00:15:12,704
THIS WHOLE SNEAKING AROUND
BEHIND THEIR BACKS THING?

374
00:15:12,788 --> 00:15:14,122
IT IS KINDA HOT.

375
00:15:17,334 --> 00:15:17,918
WE'RE GOOD.

376
00:15:20,003 --> 00:15:21,672
(PASSIONATE KISSING)

377
00:15:30,180 --> 00:15:31,473
(HEAVY KISSING)

378
00:15:37,229 --> 00:15:39,231
(UNCOMFORTABLE SMIRK)
WHOA, SLOW DOWN.

379
00:15:39,314 --> 00:15:41,024
YOU KNOW THE "ABOVE-THE-WAIST"
RULE, PETER.

380
00:15:41,108 --> 00:15:42,025
JUST RELAX.

381
00:15:42,109 --> 00:15:44,778
I'M NOT COMFORTABLE
WITH THIS.

382
00:15:44,862 --> 00:15:46,989
WHAT HAPPENED TO "I'LL MAKE IT
WORTH YOUR WHILE"?

383
00:15:47,072 --> 00:15:48,782
I MEANT I'D BUY
YOUR LIFT TICKET, STUPID!

384
00:15:48,866 --> 00:15:51,368
YOU KNOW I TOOK A VOW
OF ABSTINENCE.

385
00:15:51,451 --> 00:15:54,454
YEAH, THE PROBLEM IS,
I DIDN'T.

386
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,081
UGH...

387
00:15:56,582 --> 00:15:58,125
GET OUT.

388
00:15:58,208 --> 00:15:59,960
COME ON, DARCY.

389
00:16:03,714 --> 00:16:04,047
OUT!

390
00:16:10,345 --> 00:16:11,847
ALL RIGHT,
I'M SORRY.

391
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:14,892
MY PARENTS WERE SO RIGHT
ABOUT YOU!

392
00:16:15,851 --> 00:16:16,560
(EXHALES)

393
00:16:20,898 --> 00:16:22,399
(TRAFFIC WHIRS BY)

394
00:16:24,818 --> 00:16:26,320
(POOL BALLS CLANK)

395
00:16:28,322 --> 00:16:30,782
JOHNNY:
COMING HERE ALONE?

396
00:16:30,866 --> 00:16:32,117
THAT'S BRAVE...

397
00:16:33,243 --> 00:16:34,077
OR STUPID.

398
00:16:35,204 --> 00:16:36,580
MAYBE BOTH.

399
00:16:38,248 --> 00:16:41,168
LOOK, JOHNNY,
I DON'T WANT TO START A WAR.

400
00:16:41,251 --> 00:16:43,253
AND I THINK AS LONG AS
WE'RE UNDER THE SAME ROOF

401
00:16:43,337 --> 00:16:44,880
WE SHOULD TRY TO GET ALONG.

402
00:16:44,963 --> 00:16:48,300
THAT'S NOT WHAT
PODCAST TOBY SAID.

403
00:16:52,554 --> 00:16:55,098
YEAH,
WE'VE ALL HEARD IT.

404
00:16:56,433 --> 00:16:59,937
AND NOW BEFORE SOMEONE
MESSES WITH YOU?

405
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:03,023
I SUGGEST YOU BUST
OUTTA HERE.

406
00:17:04,107 --> 00:17:05,651
LOOK,
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND!

407
00:17:05,734 --> 00:17:07,152
I WANT TO TAKE YOU UP
ON YOUR PEACE TREATY.

408
00:17:07,236 --> 00:17:10,072
TREATY'S OFF THE TABLE,
WIENER.

409
00:17:10,155 --> 00:17:12,574
I'LL SEE YOU AT SCHOOL.

410
00:17:21,124 --> 00:17:22,626
(ROCK MUSIC PLAYS)

411
00:17:23,252 --> 00:17:25,629
(LIVELY CHATTER OF PARTYGOERS)

412
00:17:25,712 --> 00:17:27,047
CHURCH RETREAT,
SMURCH RETREAT.

413
00:17:27,130 --> 00:17:28,882
AREN'T YOU GLAD
WE CAME UP HERE?

414
00:17:28,966 --> 00:17:30,592
NOT REMOTELY.

415
00:17:32,177 --> 00:17:35,806
EASY, TIGER, BUS LEAVES
IN HALF AN HOUR.

416
00:17:35,889 --> 00:17:38,433
YOU WERE RIGHT, YOU KNOW -
ABOUT FORBIDDING THINGS.

417
00:17:38,517 --> 00:17:39,768
JUST NOW,
IN THE BEDROOM;

418
00:17:39,852 --> 00:17:43,522
PETER WAS TRYING
TO MAKE ME DO THINGS.

419
00:17:44,273 --> 00:17:47,359
ISN'T THE RULE OF ABSTINENCE
SUPPOSED TO MAKE LIFE EASIER?

420
00:17:47,442 --> 00:17:48,652
(SIGHS)
IT'S NOT A RULE.

421
00:17:48,735 --> 00:17:49,695
I'M NOT READY.

422
00:17:49,778 --> 00:17:51,822
I WANT TO WAIT
UNTIL I'M MARRIED.

423
00:17:51,905 --> 00:17:54,074
BUT I'M NOT LIKE YOU,
MANNY.

424
00:17:54,157 --> 00:17:57,327
WITH NO VALUES,
NO SELF-RESPECT.

425
00:17:58,203 --> 00:17:59,705
WELL, IF YOU'RE GONNA GET OFF
ON YOUR HIGH-HORSE,

426
00:17:59,788 --> 00:18:01,248
THEN I'M GONE.

427
00:18:01,331 --> 00:18:03,542
YOU AND SATAN JR.
ARE MADE FOR EACH OTHER.

428
00:18:03,625 --> 00:18:06,128
(MUSIC PLAYS)
(LIVELY CHATTER)

429
00:18:12,676 --> 00:18:13,427
(BANGS ON DOOR)

430
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:14,678
I HAVE TO PEE!

431
00:18:25,856 --> 00:18:26,815
SAV:
HEY, MAN.

432
00:18:26,899 --> 00:18:28,400
GETTIN' YOUR SHINE ON?

433
00:18:28,483 --> 00:18:30,819
WHATEVER, MAN.
SUE ME.

434
00:18:31,737 --> 00:18:33,030
(BOTTLES CLANK)

435
00:18:39,745 --> 00:18:41,246
(ROCK MUSIC PLAYS)

436
00:18:43,332 --> 00:18:45,042
(OVERLAPPING CHATTER)

437
00:18:55,719 --> 00:18:58,889
I'M A JACKASS.
SORRY. JACK-BUTT.

438
00:18:59,389 --> 00:19:00,557
(LAUGHS)

439
00:19:02,434 --> 00:19:04,436
HOW WASTED
ARE YOU?

440
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:07,147
(SLURRED SPEECH)
I ONLY HAS ONE DRINK,
JACK-ASS!

441
00:19:07,231 --> 00:19:08,649
OOH, SAUCY!

442
00:19:10,359 --> 00:19:11,652
YOU'RE A BAD
LIAR THOUGH.

443
00:19:11,735 --> 00:19:13,111
EVEN WORSE
WHEN YOU'RE DRUNK.

444
00:19:13,195 --> 00:19:14,321
(EXHALES)

445
00:19:14,404 --> 00:19:15,906
LET'S NOT...

446
00:19:16,740 --> 00:19:19,576
LET'S NOT FIGHT
ANY MORE, OKAY?

447
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:21,662
DEAL.
PINKIE SWEAR?

448
00:19:26,083 --> 00:19:28,877
WE CAN GO DO IT
IF YOU WANT.

449
00:19:28,961 --> 00:19:30,128
DO WHAT?

450
00:19:30,671 --> 00:19:33,507
WHATEVER.
ANYTHING YOU WANT.

451
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:37,803
CAN I TELL YOU
A SECRET?

452
00:19:40,931 --> 00:19:43,183
I'M A VIRGIN TOO.

453
00:19:43,267 --> 00:19:44,726
BUT I DON'T CARE,
YOU KNOW.

454
00:19:44,810 --> 00:19:47,563
I'LL...
WAIT 'TIL WHENEVER.

455
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:49,815
'CUZ... I LOVE YOU.

456
00:19:57,197 --> 00:19:59,116
AND I'M GONNA BARF.

457
00:20:01,994 --> 00:20:04,162
(MUSIC BLARES)

458
00:20:12,629 --> 00:20:13,964
TOBY:
(SNIFFLES)

459
00:20:15,382 --> 00:20:16,049
HEY, JT.

460
00:20:16,967 --> 00:20:18,260
I KNOW YOU'RE BUSY,

461
00:20:18,343 --> 00:20:19,678
BUT UM,

462
00:20:19,761 --> 00:20:21,138
IF I HAD ANYONE ELSE
TO TALK TO, I WOULD.

463
00:20:24,933 --> 00:20:25,559
(SIGHS)

464
00:20:30,981 --> 00:20:32,733
I MISS YOU, JT.

465
00:20:33,609 --> 00:20:37,112
AND I KNOW VIOLENCE
JUST MULTIPLIES VIOLENCE

466
00:20:37,196 --> 00:20:39,698
IN THE DEEP,
DARK SOMETHING,

467
00:20:39,781 --> 00:20:40,949
BUT... (SIGHS)

468
00:20:42,659 --> 00:20:44,870
IT SUCKS THAT THE LAKEHURST
PEOPLE ARE IN OUR HALLS

469
00:20:44,953 --> 00:20:46,413
AND YOU'RE NOT.

470
00:20:46,496 --> 00:20:48,832
